-- EDITING IMAGES

The images are regular ARGB png files.  The alpha part is applied during the
rendering.

Note that first 4 pixels from each image on row 112 are used as a drawing colors
for GUI.. The colors are:
		CLR_MENU_BG		= 0,		/**< menu background */
		CLR_MENU_FONT		= 1,		/**< menu font color */
		CLR_EXCEPTION_FONT	= 2,		/**< exceptions font color */
		CLR_ANNOUNCEMENT_FONT	= 3,		/**< announcement font color */


# vim: set tw=80:
